{"success":true,"result":{"Q_10108208566764-3":{"resources":[],"questions":[{"id":"Q_10108208566764-3","subjectId":101,"knowledgePoints":null,"knowledgePointsNew":[],"testMethods":[{"id":"TM_10100000673226","main":1}],"solutionMethods":[],"resourceIds":null,"resourceIndex":0,"listenUrl":null,"listenName":null,"listenSeconds":0,"exploreSeconds":0,"answersSeconds":0,"paperIds":["P_10100122723426-9","P_10100122723426-10","P_10100122723426-11","P_10100122723426-12"],"books":null,"booksNew":null,"contentTypeId":1010008,"contentType2Id":0,"difficultyInt":3,"description":"阅读课外文章，回答问题","notFitMobile":0,"seconds":420,"complex":1,"nid":null,"lastEditorId":null,"finalAuditorId":null,"roughAuditorIds":null,"content":{"content":"<p style=\"text-indent: 2em; text-align: center;\"><strong>她是我的朋友</strong><br></p><p style=\"text-indent: 2em;\">战争时期，有一天，几发炮弹落在一所孤儿院里。两名儿童当场被炸死。还有几名儿童受了伤，其中有个小姑娘。</p><p style=\"text-indent: 2em;\">附近医院的医生和护士接到消息，带着救护用品迅速赶到了现场。经过查看，他们确认这个小姑娘伤得最重，如果不立刻抢救，这个小女孩就会因为休克和流血过多而死去。</p><p style=\"text-indent: 2em;\">输血迫在眉睫。医生和护士都不具有和她相符的血型。几名未受伤的孤儿却可以给她输血。一位女医生告诉这几个孤儿，如果他们不能补足这个小姑娘失去的血，她一定会死去，问是否有人愿意献血。</p><p style=\"text-indent: 2em;\">一阵沉默之后，一只小手颤抖地举起来。忽然又放下去，然后又举起来。 </p><p style=\"text-indent: 2em;\">“噢，谢谢你。”医生说，“你叫什么名字？”</p><p style=\"text-indent: 2em;\">“阮恒。”</p><p style=\"text-indent: 2em;\">那个叫阮恒的小男孩很快地躺在草垫上。他的胳膊用酒精擦拭后，一根针扎进他的血管。抽血过程中阮恒一动不动，一句话也不说。</p><p style=\"text-align: left; text-indent: 2em;\">过了一会儿，他突然啜泣了一下，全身颤抖并迅速用另一只手捂住脸。“疼吗，阮恒？”医生问道。阮恒摇摇头。但过了一会儿，他又开始呜咽，并再一次试图用手掩盖他的痛苦。医生又问是不是针刺疼了他，他又摇了摇头。</p><p style=\"text-indent: 2em;\">接着，<span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">他那不时的啜泣变成持续不断的低声哭泣。他眼睛紧闭着，用牙咬着自己的小拳头，想竭力制止抽泣。</span></p><p style=\"text-indent: 2em;\">医生问他为什么这样哭，然后用轻柔的声音安慰他。男孩立刻停止了哭泣，好像刚才什么事也没有发生一样。</p><p style=\"text-indent: 2em;\">事后，医生对周围的人说：“他是以为自己就要死了。他想准会让他把所有的血都给那个小姑娘，好让她活下来。”</p><p style=\"text-indent: 2em;\">“但是他为什么愿意这样做呢？”有人问。</p><p style=\"text-indent: 2em;\">医生转过身向小男孩提出同样的问题。小男孩回答说：“她是我的朋友。”</p>","contentDesc":"","analysis":"","subContents":[{"content":"根据解释从文中找出词语。<p style=\"white-space: normal;\">比喻事情已到眼前，非常紧迫。__$$__</p>","answers":[{"answer":"迫在眉睫","subAnswers":["迫在眉睫"],"richTexts":null,"scorePercentage":1,"classification":"","knowledgePoints":null,"knowledgePointsNew":[{"id":"KP_10100078310597","tagId":0,"main":1,"featureIds":[]}],"testMethods":[],"solutionMethods":[],"classificationListenUrl":null}],"subContentTypeId":4,"analysis":"","optionType":"word","options":[],"hideOptionNumber":0,"listenUrl":"","listenName":"","listenSeconds":0,"exploreSeconds":0,"answersSeconds":0,"oralDict":{"seconds":null,"variables":null,"keywords":null,"options":null,"voiceText":null,"sentencePatterns":null,"picUrl":null,"picName":null,"beginListenUrl":null,"endListenUrl":null,"scorePercentage":null,"readySeconds":null,"listenFile":null,"contentDesc":null,"answers":null,"voiceTextsNew":null,"jsgf":null,"videoUrl":null,"videoCoverUrl":null,"highlightPos":null},"submitWays":[0],"tags":[101006],"analysisList":null,"pictureUrl":"","extras":{},"tagsDesc":["其他"]},{"content":"文中画线句运用了神态和__$$__描写。","answers":[{"answer":"动作","subAnswers":["动作"],"richTexts":null,"scorePercentage":1,"classification":"","knowledgePoints":null,"knowledgePointsNew":[],"testMethods":[],"solutionMethods":[],"classificationListenUrl":null}],"subContentTypeId":4,"analysis":"","optionType":"word","options":[],"hideOptionNumber":0,"listenUrl":"","listenName":"","listenSeconds":0,"exploreSeconds":0,"answersSeconds":0,"oralDict":{"seconds":null,"variables":null,"keywords":null,"options":null,"voiceText":null,"sentencePatterns":null,"picUrl":null,"picName":null,"beginListenUrl":null,"endListenUrl":null,"scorePercentage":null,"readySeconds":null,"listenFile":null,"contentDesc":null,"answers":null,"voiceTextsNew":null,"jsgf":null,"videoUrl":null,"videoCoverUrl":null,"highlightPos":null},"submitWays":[0],"tags":[101007],"analysisList":null,"pictureUrl":"","extras":{},"tagsDesc":["其他"]}]},"docId":"Q_10108208566764","version":3,"wordId":null,"pictureUrl":